		<link>http://www.godlessgirl.com/2011/09/c-s-lewis-and-reality/</link>
		<comments>http://www.godlessgirl.com/2011/09/c-s-lewis-and-reality/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Fri, 02 Sep 2011 15:34:07 +0000</pubDate>
